Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:44.18,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}在满是人影的街道尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.46,OP_CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}有你在那里
